my-claw/sdp/prd-federation.md:| FD-010 | Add `promptclaw init` federation setup — on project init, generate keypair and create identity. Add `--join-network` flag to request joining an existing instance's network. | T1 |
my-claw/sdp/prd-federation.md:| FD-014 | Write comprehensive tests: identity signing/verification round-trip, permission evaluation (all role x visibility combinations), message serialization, replay protection, delegation lifecycle, sync conflict resolution. TDD — tests first. | T2 |
